text: @MSNBC COVID-19 has stirred Trump to campaign for himself. Historians know that preparedness was ended by Calvin Coolidge. There exists a government stockpile waiting for a country of its own. There are fifty independent states and FEMA bidding for medical supplies, perhaps on eBay.
